&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staff Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Band 5&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Based at St Margaret’s Hospital, Epping, Essex&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 Registered Nurses to join our well-established service delivering high quality patient centred care. Plane Ward is a 22 bedded Elderly Rehabilitation Ward based in St Margaret’s Hospital, Epping, Essex.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and proactive nurses, eager to develop their skills within Elderly care. The successful candidate will work under the direction of the Senior Charge Nurse and must be able to demonstrate good leadership skills and be committed to providing high quality person-centred care for our patients involving the patients and carers/relatives. They will be part of a Multi-disciplinary Team enabling patients to achieve their optimum level of independence on the ward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity for personal development and is suitable for qualified registered nurses and newly qualified staff nurses are welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is open for Registered Nurses and is not suitable for RMN’s&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Livingstone Nhanga Job title Ward Manager Email address livingstone.nhanga@nhs.net Telephone number 01279 827205 / 07773948414&lt;/p&gt;
